These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  nurse, chef, writer, lawyer, librarian, pilot, social-worker
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, board-games, card-games, cooking, gardening, hiking, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is the chef##1
 2. the pilot is on the right of the librarian##1
 3. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
 4. the writer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the chef##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the lawyer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 9. the nurse is on the left of the writer##1
10. the librarian is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
13. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
14. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
15. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
16. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
17. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
18. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6     |      7      |
| Job    | social-worker    | librarian  | pilot       | chef | nurse | writer | lawyer        |
| Hobby   | gardening | hiking | card-games | baking    | writing   | cooking   | board-games |

