.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: salsa, soul, house, blues, gospel, trance, techno
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bike, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter, tram, trike
 1. the person driving the bike is the fan of soul##1
 2. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
 3. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the motorbike and the fan of techno##2
 4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 6. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of house##1
 8. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
10. the person driving the motorbike is the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of blues##1
13. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
14. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
15. the fan of blues is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |       3       |     4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre       | techno | house | gospel | trance | blues | salsa | soul |
| Transport   | trike   | scooter    | motorbike     | tram      | airplane     | quad-bike   | bike    |

