.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-4::.
7 different games are played: bridge, domino, mah-jongg, billiard, backgammon, go, monopoly
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, fish, mouse, rabbit, rat, snake
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 6. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
 8. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
 9. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
10. the owner of the rabbit is between the person playing bridge and the person playing domino##2
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person playing go##1
12. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
13. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
14. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
15. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
16. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |   5    |   6    |   7   |
| Game   | go | monopoly    | billiard | mah-jongg | bridge | backgammon    | domino |
| Pet           | snake       | chinchilla | bird   | fish    | rat    | rabbit | mouse |

