The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, november, may, august, july, march, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
 5. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
10. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
12. the person watching disaster movies is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching horror movies##2
13. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
14. the person watching family movies is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person watching superhero movies##2
15. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
16. the person watching western movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
