 4. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 5. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
10. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
11. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking fanta is the person playing domino##1
13. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4      |        5        |      6      |       7       |
| Beverage   | milk     | lemonade   | mirinda | sprite     | fanta           | tea         | hot-chocolate |
| Game        | backgammon | monopoly | go | mah-jongg | domino | scrabble | billiard     |

